  "dispute_letter": "Dear Billing Department,\n\nI am writing to dispute charges on my account ER-9921 from 2025-10-12.\n\nFirst, I noticed that a Basic Metabolic Panel (CPT 80048) was billed in addition to a Comprehensive Metabolic Panel (CPT 80053). Under NCCI guidelines, these codes are mutually exclusive, as the BMP is a clinical subset of the CMP. I respectfully request the removal of the $150.00 charge for the BMP.\n\nFurthermore, the charge of $2,500.00 for the Level 5 ER visit (99285) greatly exceeds fair market rates for this area, which typically range around $600-$1000. I request a review of these charges.\n\nThank you,\nAlex Smith",
